- 'More frequently used functions' indicates a higher call count; 
- 'Top three slower performance records' refers to the highest three execution times for each function;
- 'Average duration' is calculated across all successful executions of each function.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT functions.name, functions.description
FROM functions
JOIN error_logs ON functions.function_id = error_logs.function_id;
